Enjoy spending time in the sunroom overlooking the lush open space surrounded by mature trees and wildlife. Amazing yard with firepit, landscaping, and a deck with glass panels and a built-in hot tub that overlooks the yard.

description:
Recently sold: $399,000. Enjoy over 2 acres of lush, private serenity. This property offers mature trees,  flower gardens, and fire pit sitting area, this could be your private oasis.  As you enter the home you will be welcomed by the  oversized entryway, plenty of room for all the Minnesota seasonal attire!   The kitchen is adorn with wood cabinets, stainless steel appliances, a beautiful bay window,  a large island surrounded by an abundance of natural light. The kitchen opens up to the Living Room that overlooks the beautiful backyard.  The open kitchen/living room is a great space for entertaining. This space also leads to the backyard off the large covered porch where you can enjoy the views of the backyard from the porch swing.  There is gorgeous wide plank Oak floors throughout the main floor.  The home offers 3 bedrooms on one level.  The home has a unique 24x20 room with its own entrance, uses for this space are unlimited; could be used as a home office, a master bedroom, hobby room or just a large sun room or plant area for those with a green thumb.  The lower level also offers a large recreation room that has many possibilities.  
The home has a 2 car attached garage, and also a detached 3 car garage with a loft.  The detached 3 car garage has its own driveway and offers plenty of extra parking for toys!  Above the 3 car garage is a loft that can be finished to your desires, or as is for a great storage area.

The main level of this charming walkout rambler for sale in Oak Grove also includes three bedrooms--one of which is the master suite w/private bath and walk-in closet, another full bathroom and a laundry room! The finished/walkout LL includes a family room w/projector and screen--great for family movie nights, 4th bedroom, hobby room/non-conforming 5th bedroom, office space and another full bath w/jetted tub!

Additional amenities of this Oak Grove home for sale include: cul-de-sac location, asphalt driveway, walk-in closets in bedroom 2 and bedroom 4, LaView camera surveillance system, tons of storage plus more!

Contact Chuck Carstensen with Re/Max Results at 612-290-3809 to setup your showing today!

description:
Recently sold: $469,900. Every great recipe comes from quality ingredients. The same can be true for quality homes and this one does not disappoint! 
Starting with the garage - the heated floors are covered with a poly aspartic epoxy for long-lasting durability, 10 ft garage doors, hot and cold running water, floor drains, and is accessible from the extra wide asphalt driveway. 
Steel and stone beautify the exterior of this home and is breathtaking in the evening by the soft glow of the soffit lighting. Surrounding the lavish rock and mulch landscaping is expertly applied concrete edging. The stamped and colored concrete patio allows for a glimpse of the wildlife running through the nearly 6 acres! Get the smores ready at the fire pit that overlooks the pond. 
Travertine floors are heated and meander through the gorgeous kitchen complete with Craftsman trim, granite counters, a walk-in pantry, a brand new refrigerator, and optimal recessed lighting. 
Surround sound can be heard from the large living/dining room, the family room with a wet bar and dishwasher, and all the way to the patio! 
After a long day, get away from it all in the Master Suite. The race track ceiling in the bedroom gives a calming texture to the space, a walk-in cultured marble tiled shower, huge vanity, make up table and a whirlpool tub complete this sanctuary. 
Having overnight guests? A Princess Suite is the perfect accommodation and privacy. 
Other quality ingredients include an air exchanger, upper-level laundry, central vac, shaker style Alder doors, hand textured ceilings, and Hunter Douglas automatic blinds. 
Quality ingredients make this a recipe that everyone will enjoy! 
Brought to you by the Chris Fritch Team Keller Williams Classic Realty 763-746-3997
